headline: QUALCOMM (NasdaqGS:QCOM) Engages Multiple Co-Lead Underwriters For US$500 Million Fixed-Income Offerings
summary: On May 19, 2025, QUALCOMM (NasdaqGS:QCOM) announced changes to its fixed-income offerings, incorporating renowned financial institutions as co-lead underwriters. These changes align with the company's recent stock price movement, which increased by 12% over the past month, as the broader market rose 2%. headline: Advantech's Tsai on Business AI Integration Outlook
